### 5.4 Contenido inicial de `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Virtual environment
.venv/
venv/

# Python cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Environment variables
.env

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Windows
Thumbs.db

# Reports and generated files
reports/*.html
reports/*.png
reports/*.csv

# IDEs and editors
.vscode/
.idea/
